         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16 December 1874. ¶ Revered Patron and friend, ¶  ¶ I take the liberty to request ¶  ¶ that you [,,,] ¶ German text illegible. ¶  ¶ me one copy of the 'Map of part of the colony of West Australia, sho...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">74.12.16</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From August Petermann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Sammlung Perthes Archiv,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">SPA ARCH<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">PGM<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">328</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Forschungsbibliothek Gotha der Universität Erfurt.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS a letterpress copy. For a published version of this letter, see Voigt (1996), p. 127.</p>
               </note>16. Dez. 74.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochverehrter Gönner und Freund,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich erlaube mir, Sie zu bitten, mir 1 Exp. von "Map of part of the colony of West Australia, showing the progress of the geol. survey from Aug. 1870 to June 1872, by H. Y. L. Brown, Melbourne 1873", gütigst aus [...]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">illegible word</seg>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>u. unter Band überschicken zu wollen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Karten<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>der nächsten Reisen von Ross u<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Forrest werden mich auch ungeheuer interessiren.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin Ihnen für so viele gütige Sendungen Dank schuldig, dass ich beschämt bin und von meiner Schuld kaum zu sprechen wage.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Auch die grosse Güte, nach mir eine hervorragende Bergkette zu benennen, hat mich tief gerührt und bitte ich Sie, auch dem ausgezeichneten Herrn Giles, den es wiederum Ihr Verdienst ist, entdeckt, protegirt und angeheuert zu haben,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>meinen Dank<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">omitted</seg>?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>auszudrücken. Bei der ersten Gelegenheit, die ich haben werde, Neue Namen auf die Karte zu setzen, können Sie Sich versichert halten, dass ich meines hohen Gönners in den Antipoden, meines verehrten australischen Humboldts, nicht vergessen und auch des liebenswürdigen Herrn Giles gedenken werde.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">In grösster Eile</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>aber alter treuer Anhänglichkeit,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ergebenheit u. Dankbarkeit<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A. Petermann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Ich bitte Herrn Giles meine Photographie gütigst zu vermitteln, sehr stolz würde ich auf die seinige sein.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">16 December 1874.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Revered Patron and friend,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I take the liberty to request<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that you [,,,]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">German text illegible</seg>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>me one copy of the 'Map of part of the colony of West Australia, showing the progress of the geological survey from August<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1870 to June 1872', by H. Y. L. Brown, Melbourne, 1873,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The map, by the WA Government Geologist, Henry Y. L. Brown,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was published in Perth, WA, not Melbourne. Digitized versions are available: uncoloured at<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <ref target="https://archive.sro.wa.gov.au/uploads/r/srowa/a/e/aebc1bb2887a1faee076ede9ce7ac7cd50f34f3aea707e48531a15a41d88f77a/3423-208.jpg">https://archive.sro.wa.gov.au/uploads/r/srowa/a/e/aebc1bb2887a1faee076ede9ce7ac7cd50f34f3aea707e48531a15a41d88f77a/3423-208.jpg</ref>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>and coloured at<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <ref target="http://purl.slwa.wa.gov.au/slwa_b1763405_1.jpg">http://purl.slwa.wa.gov.au/slwa_b1763405_1.jpg</ref>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(both accessed 15 April 2019).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and send it to me as printed matter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The maps of the next expeditions of Ross and Forrest<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In 1874, John Ross was engaged by Thomas Elder to lead an exploring expedition west<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Peake station<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on the Overland Telegraph Line, SA, in the hope of eventually reaching Perth, but was eventually forced back; see. 'Mr J. Ross's Explorations, 1874',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">South Australian Parliamentary Papers</seg>, 1875, No 67.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>That was, however,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ross’s<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>last expedition.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>In the same year, John Forrest successfully crossed from the west coast, at Geraldton, to the Overland Telegraph Line; however, he too undertook no further major expeditions.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>would also be of enormous interest to me.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I owe you thanks<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for so many kind transmissions<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that I feel ashamed and hardly dare to speak of my guilt.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The great kindness of naming an eminent mountain range<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Petermann Ranges, Central Australia.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>after me, too, has touched me deeply, and I beg that you will express my gratitude also to the excellent Mr Giles,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn7" n="8">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ernest Giles.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>where again it is to your merit to have discovered him, to have made him your protégé, and to have employed him. At the first opportunity<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have to place new names on the map, you may rest assured<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that I shall not forget my eminent patron in the antipodes, my revered Australian Humboldt,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn8" n="9">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Home (1998).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and that I shall also remember the amiable Mr Giles.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">In greatest haste,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>but in old faithful attachment,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>humility, and gratitude,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A. Petermann.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I beg<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>kindly to forward my photograph to Mr Giles, and should be proud to have his.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
